{
  "texts": [
    "The size of the accessible plant data sets is consequently quite modest.",
    "Only a few papers have submitted thousands of pictures for investigation (Barbedo et al.2016; Sladojevic et al. 2016; Meunkaewjinda et al. 2008; Pires et al. 2016; Shrivastava et al. 2019; Schikora et al. 2012).",
    "The photographs in the database are taken under extremely restricted environmental settings.",
    "In order to make the algorithms more useful, photos must be collected under real-world circumstances.",
    "The current situation calls for effective picture acquisition of leaf images."
  ]
}